data.description: This great pool home needs a little TLC but will make a fantastic home located in the Ashton Elementary, Sarasota Middle and Sarasota High school districts. This 3-bedroom 2 bath home provides a large back yard, is adjacent to county easements providing even more green space. You have ultimate privacy as the last house on the block. The open floorplan allows for easy entertaining from the living room to dining to family area. The covered patio provides a respite and a great place to relax while the family enjoys the pool. This would make a fantastic rental if you are looking for a great investment. You are minutes from shopping, downtown Sarasota and minutes from the crystal white sand beaches of Siesta Key.
